Firstly, I am asked reason for replacement,I opted for Lost. Secondly ,after giving the reason,i observed my old card is replaced with New Card number and here I saw the bug. title: Deposit and withdrawal process change for pots Feature
content: Phoenix (SURAJ SAHOO) 28 April 2025 05:50 1 I just recently got to know about a change in the process for depositing and withdrawal, to and from pots. Previously we’d have to use mPin for either one but and the amount reflected almost instantly in either account or pot, but now to deposit we need to use UPI pin… Which is fine, the problem is with withdrawal There’s no verification on withdrawal, Withdrawal will happen through NEFT which will take upto 2hrs… So even to withdraw a small amount we may have to wait upto 2hrs… This is too inconvenient… 4 Likes
